">\n<div>\n<a class=\"product-title\" href=\"https://www.adafruit.com/product/3221\">Mini Panel Mount SPDT Toggle Switch</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"product-price\">$0.95</div>\n<a aria-live=\"polite\" class=\"product-buy btn-primary\" data-name=\"Mini Panel Mount SPDT Toggle Switch\" data-pid=\"3221\" data-qty=\"1\" href=\"https://www.adafruit.com/product/3221\" id=\"3221-product\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">Add  to Cart</a>\n</div>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n</nav>\n</div>\n<div class=\"right-content\">\n<div class=\"badges headline-badges\">\n<div aria-label=\"This many users have saved this guide\" class=\"badge favorites-count\" title=\"Saves\">\n        11\n      </div>\n<div aria-label=\"This is a new guide\" class=\"badge new\">\n        New\n      </div>\n<div aria-label=\"Guide skill level\" class=\"badge skill-level\" title=\"Skill Level\">\n      Intermediate\n    </div>\n<div aria-label=\"Guide type\" class=\"badge skill-level\" title=\"Guide Type\">\n      Project guide\n    </div>\n<turbo-frame id=\"display_reactions\">\n<span class=\"reactions\">\n<form accept-charset=\"UTF-8\" action=\"/guides/4509/reactions/toggle_reaction\" data-controller=\"reactions\" method=\"post\"><input name=\"_method\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"put\"/><input name=\"authenticity_token\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"nrukudj5oU8r98fCepkx2q7pW2cOF__Orvojj8vcEfSIuSLMjeOOkEao83jFS9w3y7ONqwQV8j9xmribfRwrNw\"/>\n<div class=\"reaction\">\n<span class=\"emoji\">😍</span>\n<span class=\"count\">1</span>\n</div>\n<div class=\"reaction\">\n<span class=\"emoji\">🔥</span>\n<span class=\"count\">2</span>\n</div>\n</form> </span>\n</turbo-frame>\n</div>\n<h2 aria-label=\"Page title\">\n<span id=\"overview\">Overview</span>\n</h2>\n<div class=\"page-content\">\n<div aria-label=\"Page content\" class=\"\" role=\"region\">\n<div class=\"element image-element\">\n<a href=\"/assets/143743\">\n<video aria-label=\"arduino_compatibles_handshake.gif\" loop=\"loop\" muted=\"muted\" playsinline=\"\" poster=\"https://cdn-learn.adafruit.com/assets/assets/000/143/743/medium800thumb/arduino_compatibles_handshake.jpg?1776181556\" preload=\"auto\"></video>&gt;\n          <source data-src=\"https://cdn-learn.adafruit.com/assets/assets/000/143/743/large1024mp4/arduino_compatibles_handshake.mp4?1776181556\"/>\n<source data-src=\"https://cdn-learn.adafruit.com/assets/assets/000/143/743/large1024webm/arduino_compatibles_handshake.webm?1776181556\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp8,vorbis\"/>\n          Your browser does not support the video tag.\n        \n</a> </div>\n<div class=\"text-element\">\n<p>Ditch the smart phone and communicate with your buddy by building this set of walkie talkies! A Feather ESP32-S3 Reverse TFT runs Arduino code that uses the <a href=\"https://www.espressif.com/en/solutions/low-power-solutions/esp-now\" target=\"_blank\">ESP-NOW wireless protocol</a> to send and receive I2S audio packets, up to 10 seconds each. The w.FL antenna adds extra range to communicate at longer distances indoors or outdoors.</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"side-element\">\n<div class=\"side-images\">\n<div class=\"anchor-anchor\">\n<a class=\"anchor-link\" href=\"#step-3218622\"><span class=\"fa fa-link\"></span></a>\n</div>\n<span class=\"anchor-link-target\" id=\"step-3218622\"></span>\n<a class=\"side-image-link\" href=\"/assets/143755\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"143755-asset medium-side-image\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://cdn-learn.adafruit.com/assets/assets/000/143/755/medium640/arduino_compatibles_edited_P1490595.jpg?1776183571\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"side-text\"><div class=\"text\">\n<p>The case design is inspired by toy walkie talkies that were ubiquitous in the early-1990s. The LED button on the side acts as a status indicator when pairing or sending and receiving messages. The onboard TFT shows status messages, such as MAC address, signal strength and packet status.</p>\n</div></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"embed-element\">\n<div class=\"build-video\"><lite-youtube params=\"feature=oembed\" style=\"background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,');\" videoid=\"seLpJI3cW94\">\n<a class=\"lty-playbtn\" href=\"https://youtube.com/shorts/seLpJI3cW94\" title=\"ESP-NOW Walkie Talkies #adafruit\">\n<span class=\"lyt-visually-hidden\">Play Video: ESP-NOW Walkie Talkies #adafruit</span>\n</a>\n</lite-youtube>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"text-element\">\n<h2>\n<div class=\"anchor-anchor\">\n<a class=\"anchor-link\" href=\"#parts-3218354\"><span class=\"fa fa-link\"></span></a><span class=\"anchor-link-target\" id=\"parts-3218354\"></span>\n</div>Parts</h2>\n<p>The parts listed below are what is needed to build one walkie talkie. You will need to build two walkie talkies for this project to work.</p>\n</div>\n<div aria-labelledby=\"product-title-6303\" class=\"product-element first\" data-product-id=\"6303\">\n<input class=\"product-json\" id=\"product_analytics_6303\" name=\"product_analytics_6303\" type=\"hidden\" value='{\n  \"item_list_id\": \"4509:31790\",\n  \"item_list_name\": \"esp-now-walkie-talkies/overview\",\n  \"items\": {\n    \"item_id\": 6303,\n    \"item_name\": \"Adafruit ESP32-S3 Reverse TFT with w.FL Antenna\",\n    \"affiliation\": \"Inline Product\"\n  }\n}'/>\n<div class=\"product-column product-image\">\n<img alt=\"Angled Shot of the Adafruit ESP32-S3 Reverse TFT with w.FL Antenna.\" class=\"image-preview product-asset\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://cdn-shop.adafruit.com/640x480/6303-01.jpg\"/>\n</div>\n<div class=\"product-column product-details-wrapper\">\n<div class=\"product-details\">\n<div class=\"product-title\" id=\"product-title-6303\"><a class=\"product-link\" href=\"https://www.adafruit.com/product/6303\">Adafruit ESP32-S3 Reverse TFT with w.FL Antenna</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"product-description\">Like Missy Elliot, we like to \"put our [Feather] down, flip it and reverse it\" and that's exactly what...</div>\n<a class=\"small\" href=\"/products/6303/guides\">guides with product</a>\n